lead_paragraph: Nico Rosberg has been assured his ongoing contract negotiations with Formula One champions Mercedes will not be affected by Sunday's Austrian Grand Prix collision with team mate Lewis Hamilton.

headline.print_headline: Rosberg Contract Talks Unaffected by Crash-Mercedes
headline.main: Rosberg Contract Talks Unaffected by Crash-Mercedes
